{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d63df28dcb","title":"两条路线斗争的基本问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"92d9f0d55b","index":0,"year":1967,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"d63df28dcb"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b2012c0b4","name":"革命三结合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"0b6d8a885e","name":"革命委员会","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"1ae024ca96","name":"革命大联合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"70a1e48626","name":"军队支左","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"877762393f","name":"两条路线斗争","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"aa048f8141","name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f6514f0b9f","type":"paragraph","text":"有代表性的、有无产阶级权威的临时权力机构。这个权力机构的名称，叫革命委员会好。","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d63df28dcb"},{"id":"4a5557f750","type":"paragraph","text":"从上至下，凡要夺权的单位，都要有军队代表或民兵代表参加，组成“三结合”，不论工厂、农村、财贸、文教（大、中、小学）、党政机关及民众团体都要这样做。县以上都派军队代表，公社以下都派民兵代表，这是非常之好的。军队代表不足，可以暂缺，将来再派。","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d63df28dcb"},{"id":"3cf548d3c8","type":"paragraph","text":"关于重队要协同地方管工业的指示","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d63df28dcb"},{"id":"9d8795adff","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年三月三日）","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d63df28dcb"},{"id":"36ceb03f5a","type":"paragraph","text":"此件可印发军级会议各同志。军队不但要协同地方管农业，对工业也要管。沈阳军区派大批人员进厂做宣传和做调查的办法是很多的。××军在无锡、××军在重庆、××军在伊春、河等处也有好的经验。总之，军队不能坐视工业生产下降而置之不理。","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d63df28dcb"},{"id":"81c1ad7eb7","type":"paragraph","text":"两条路斗争的基本间题","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d63df28dcb"},{"id":"1a4bb55063","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年三月）","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d63df28dcb"},{"id":"6973a42ceb","type":"paragraph","text":"我们党内两条路线斗争，基本问题是在无产阶级夺取政权以后，即新民主主义革命胜利以后，中国究竟走资本主义道路，还是走社会主义道路的问题。资产阶级要走资本主义道路，这是很明显的。在我们共产党内部，我们要走社会主义道路；但有一部分人却认为中国是个很穷困的国家，中国资本主义发展水平很低，不能发展社会主义，必须在一段时间内走资本主义道路，然后再走社会主义道路。","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d63df28dcb"},{"id":"0daa9052dc","type":"paragraph","text":"走什么道路问题，解放初期有这个问题，现在仍然有这个问题。苏联搞了五十多年，仍是这个问题。","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d63df28dcb"},{"id":"b037fd470a","type":"paragraph","text":"对铁道兵党委一个报告（渡口厨重支左经融）的批示","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d63df28dcb"},{"id":"282b2ea097","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年三月七日）林彪、恩来、文革小组；","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d63df28dcb"},{"id":"1df69ff1a6","type":"paragraph","text":"此件似可转发全国全军，参照执行。请的处。","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d63df28dcb"},{"id":"92e85af104","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d63df28dcb"},{"id":"88eefecca0","type":"paragraph","text":"三月七日对《天津延安中学以教学班为基础实现全校大联合","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d63df28dcb"},{"id":"a49f948ac4","type":"paragraph","text":"和整顿巩固发展缸卫兵的体会》一交件的批","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d63df28dcb"},{"id":"05f2773b10","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年三月七日）林彪、恩来、文革小组各同志","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d63df28dcb"},{"id":"131d4c66a0","type":"paragraph","text":"0295","index":16,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d63df28dcb"}],"page":{"id":"cc834efdfb","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d63df28dcb","start":308,"end":308}}}},"__N_SSG":true}